sourcesContent: const StudentRow = ({ student, index, isEditing, isBooking, editData, setEditData, setEditingIndex, setBookingIndex, handleEditClick, handleBookClick, handleSave, handleVaccinationSave, handleDelete, handleMarkAsVaccinated }) => { const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setEditData(prev => ({ ...prev, [name]: value })); }; return ( {isEditing ? ( <> {student.studentId} {student.bookingStatus} {student.vaccinationName} {student.vaccinationDate} {student.vaccinationStatus} ) : isBooking ? ( <> {student.name} {student.class} {student.studentId} {student.bookingStatus} {student.vaccinationStatus} ) : ( <> {student.name} {student.class} {student.studentId} {student.bookingStatus} {student.vaccinationName} {student.vaccinationDate} {student.vaccinationStatus} )} ); }; export default StudentRow;
